<para id="para-00011">American Association of Variable Star Observers (AAVSO): <link url="https://www.aavso.org/">https://www.aavso.org/</link>. This organization of amateur astronomers helps to keep track of variable stars; its site has some background material, observing instructions, and links.</para>
