<para id="para-00016">Women in Astronomy: <link url="https://bit.ly/astronomywomen">https://bit.ly/astronomywomen</link>. A guide to readings and websites, with more about Henrietta Leavitt’s and other women’s contributions to astronomy and the obstacles they faced.</para></section>
